net.tridentsdk.world.settings

Enum GameRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<GameRule>
      • net.tridentsdk.world.settings.GameRule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<GameRule>

    public enum GameRule
extends Enum<GameRule>
    Gamerules are applied on a per-world basis and are options for more advanced/low-level properties of the world such as command blocks, drops, and inventory modifiers

    The default value for all game rules is true except for REDUCED_DEBUG_INFO and KEEP_INVENTORY, which are both false by default

    Since:
    0.4-alpha
    Author:
    The TridentSDK Team
